  "category": "character",
  "subcategory": "echo",
  "description": "All Echo frames: frame canvas 40x40px, transparent background. No outlines. No shading. No gradients. No dithering. Colors: body #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak/feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Echo occupies approx x=6..33,y=6..36 within the 40x40 canvas. Cheek patch is always present as a 3x3 block at x=24..26,y=18..20. Eyes are two 2x2 blocks at x=14..15,y=16..17 and x=22..23,y=16..17 unless the frame specifies eyes closed. Dirty: 3 frames, FPS=2, loop=true. Expression: replace normal eyes with half-closed eyes: 2x1 lines at y=17 (x=14..15 and x=22..23). Frame2 adds 2 dust pixels (#C2C3C7) at x=10,y=24 and x=29,y=23.",
